                     <p>A rather quick but clear semicursive. At the left there is a free margin of approximately 2 cm.and at the top the free margin was ay least 1.5 cm. Most of the entries have 1 (column I) or 2 (column II) heavy oblique lines in front of them indicating that they were verified.</p>
